<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.8391084>
    dc:description "FIGURE 7. Female genitalia structures of Adelidae (Nemophora basalistriata sp. nov.) and partial enlarged view of ovipositor tip (Abbreviations:AA.Apophysis anterioris; AP.Apophysis posterioris; CB. Corpus bursae; Cl. Cloaca; DB. Ductus bursae; O. Ovipositor; S8. Sternum VIII; Vb. Vestibulum; VL. Vestibular lamella)." ;
